{"tid":623421,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過喊住食飯","createTime":"2018-04-10T03:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T05:40:06.000Z","uid":104975,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c3720f84d8960722ac87f341b7099217f8bb80cc","tid":623421,"uid":104975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:45:29.000Z","msg":"平時同老豆唔講心事<br />\n有次唔開心同佢食大快活並排坐<br />\n我冇諗住講啲咩，佢主動講左句關於我唔開心既事既野<br />\n眼淚即刻流晒出黎<br />\n佢繼續懶係唔係安慰緊我咁同我講鼓勵說話<br />\n成餐飯望前面眼淚鼻涕一路流<br />\n吞落去既野其實都冇味，係一pat鼻涕加餸<br />\n個回憶好深刻，覺得自己柒得黎又好溫暖"},{"pid":"1a0c1eb7b14a2580d5fbf8cd385a9cdd1a0c393a","tid":623421,"uid":179571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:08:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd2f4480309a080be9a4dc56d617fff7d5adc1e4","tid":623421,"uid":18366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ae668bcaab37b555af45563272de0cf3aa2e38b","tid":623421,"uid":5760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:36:50.000Z","msg":"咁係咩事"},{"pid":"c438e16698dbabab595cb60f36fadd3b0c4ae69c","tid":623421,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"細個唔知衰咩 臨食飯前俾老母dup左鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1fc536953d865774b749e77f6b15cdc8109d67","tid":623421,"uid":5760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ae668bcaab37b555af45563272de0cf3aa2e38b","tid":623421,"uid":5760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:36:50.000Z","msg":"咁係咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:38:36.000Z","msg":"利申 冇試過食飯喊，試過喺街同朋友講講下喊"},{"pid":"fd2757ff4ca7160f0167cf1d9849ce4b920819d6","tid":623421,"uid":167157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"分咗手有日同老豆食早餐，老豆話你唔可以再咁樣頹落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟住聽完即刻爆喊，唔岀聲咁繼續食我個熱香餅，老豆比我嚇到呆咗，大家成餐飯無再岀過聲。"},{"pid":"f0cb28fe8196252c09ea8de9efb48a513fa5042a","tid":623421,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/133809_84e9f357985e01acc1b8ab53635b7c54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F133809_84e9f357985e01acc1b8ab53635b7c54.png&h=9e4f52fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一見post名就諗起呢張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7e619421af1258d2157c8427fe85bbbcf7f725","tid":623421,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:40:06.000Z","msg":"啊女乖"}]}